ng%20win%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Sena%3B%20the%20saffron%20party%20won%20105%20seats%20(down%2017%20from%202014)%20and%20its%20ally%2056%20(down%20seven).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20two%20long-time%20allies%20fell%20out%2C%20quite%20spectacularly%2C%20in%20the%20following%20days%20after%20they%20failed%20to%20agree%20a%20power-sharing%20deal.%20Mr%20Thackeray%20then%20led%20his%20Sena%20into%20a%20surprise%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20(then%20also%20undivided)%20to%20shut%20out%20a%20furious%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20the%20surprise%20of%20many%2C%20the%20ruling%20tripartite%20alliance%20lasted%20for%20nearly%20three%20years%20despite%20the%20divergent%20political%20beliefs%20and%20ideologies%20of%20the%20Sena%20and%20the%20Congress-NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20it%20was%20an%20internal%20rebellion%20led%20by%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20that%20ousted%20the%20MVA%20government.%20Mr%20Shinde%20led%20Sena%20lawmakers%20into%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20forcing%20Mr%20Thackeray%20to%20resign%20and%20allowing%20himself%20to%20be%20named%20as%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20split%20a%20year%20later%20in%20a%20near-identical%20process%20that%20saw%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20lawmakers%20loyal%20to%20him%20joining%20the%20BJP-Shinde%20Sena%2C%20and%20he%20then%20became%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Maharashtra%20politics%20has%20been%20roiled%20in%20controversy%20that%20extended%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20heard%20petitions%20and%20cross-petitions%20on%20disqualification%20of%20MLAs%20and%2C%20in%20the%20build-up%20to%20this%20election%2C%20pleas%20on%20which%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20faction%20is%20the%20'real'%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%2