0Hemant%20Soren's%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20leading%20the%20ruling%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20faces%20a%20fierce%20challenge%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU)%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%20point%20to%20a%20narrow%20race%20with%20varying%20predictions.%20According%20to%20Matrize%2C%20the%20NDA%20is%20poised%20to%20win%2042-47%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20JMM-led%20alliance%20with%2025-30%20seats.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20TimesNow-JVC%20survey%20forecasts%2040-44%20seats%20for%20the%20NDA%2C%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20securing%2030-40%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20definitive%20projections%20come%20from%20People's%20Pulse%2C%20which%20predicts%20a%20clear%20win%20for%20the%20NDA%2C%20with%2042-48%20seats%20compared%20to%20the%20JMM's%2016-23%20seats.%20AJSU%20is%20expected%20to%20secure%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20this%20scenario.%20However%2C%20Axis%20My%20India%20and%20P%20Marq%20offer%20a%20contrasting%20view%2C%20giving%20the%20JMM-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20a%20commanding%2049-59%20and%2037-47%20seats%20respectively%2C%20while%20the%20NDA%20is%20projected%20to%20fall%20far%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20agency%20forecasting%20a%20hung%20assembly%20is%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%2C%20suggesting%20that%20both%20alliances%20will%20settle%20between%2036-40%20seats%2C%20just%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2041.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20exit%20polls%20giving%20NDA%20the%20edge%2C%20the%20JMM%20is%20confident%20of%20forming%20government%20again%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20with%20a%20two-thirds%20majority.%20The%20JMM%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20even%20struggle%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%2011%20of%20the%20state's%2024%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20on%20November%2023%2C%20our%20government%20