0incoming%20administration's%20anticipated%20deregulation%20efforts%20as%20a%20significant%20advantage%20for%20Tesla%2C%20particularly%20for%20its%20Full%20Self-Driving%20initiatives%2C%20which%20have%20faced%20regulatory%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Tesla%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20ventures%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20aerospace%20have%20further%20expanded%20his%20wealth.%20His%2060%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20xAI%2C%20a%20private%20AI%20firm%20valued%20at%20%2450%20billion%2C%20added%20%2413%20billion%20to%20his%20fortune.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%2042%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20SpaceX%2C%20valued%20at%20%24210%20billion%20in%20a%20June%20tender%20offer%2C%20contributed%20%2488%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20around%20SpaceX's%20upcoming%20funding%20round%2C%20which%20could%20value%20the%20company%20at%20%24250%20billion%2C%20suggests%20Mr%20Musk's%20net%20worth%20might%20climb%20even%20higher%2C%20potentially%20adding%20%2418%20billion%20to%20his%20fortune.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Musk's%20current%20net%20worth%20puts%20him%20%2480%20billion%20ahead%20of%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20Oracle's%20chairman%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20title%20of%20the%20world's%20second-richest%20individual%20with%20%24235%20billion.%20Most%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20wealth%20stems%20from%20his%2013%25%20stake%20in%20Tesla%2C%20currently%20valued%20at%20%24145%20billion%20and%20his%20pending%209%20per%20cent%20equity%20award%20in%20the%20company.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20despite%20his%20historic%20fortune%2C%20Tesla%20shares%20remain%20about%2014%20per%20cent%20below%20their%20all-time%20high%20from%20late%202021.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20broader%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20has%20risen%2027%20per%20cent%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732332420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2sq0h55g_elon-musk-afp-_625x300_04_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-is-the-we