0thanked%20her%20family%20including%20her%20daughter%2C%20Freya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20given%20me%20so%20much%20strength%20and%20courage%20over%20the%20last%20six%20years%20throughout%20this%20nightmare%20to%20keep%20on%20pushing%20forward%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20show%20Freya%20and%20every%20other%20girl%20and%20boy%20that%20you%20can%20stand%20up%20for%20yourself%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20you%20-%20no%20matter%20who%20the%20person%20is%20-%20and%20justice%20will%20be%20served%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcGregor%20to%20file%20an%20appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20McGregor%20said%20he%20intended%20to%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20disappointed%20that%20the%20jury%20did%20not%20hear%20all%20the%20evidence%20that%20the%20DPP%20reviewed.%20I%20am%20with%20my%20family%20now%2C%20focused%20on%20my%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20to%20all%20my%20support%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcGregor%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20stars%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Ultimate%20Fighting%20Championship%20(UFC)%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20circuit%2C%20formerly%20holding%20the%20featherweight%20and%20lightweight%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732325460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flu8m8d7o_nikita-hand_625x300_23_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nikita-hand-woman-wins-sexual-assault-case-against-mma-fighter-conor-mcgregor-7083990%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McGregor%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20stars%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Ultimate%20Fighting%20Championship%20(UFC)%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20circuit%2C%20formerly%20holding%20the%20featherweight%20and%20lightweight%20titles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22