g-to-normalize-how-to-have-them-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enever%20talk%20about%20the%20hard%20topics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20could%20make%20or%20break%20their%20future.%20Next%20thing%20you%20know%2C%20they've%20split%20up%20because%20one%20of%20them%20is%20dead%20set%20on%20kids%20and%20the%20other%20is%20dead%20set%20against%20it.%20We%20weren't%20going%20to%20let%20that%20happen%20to%20our%20love%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20said%20I%20wanted%20a%20child%20within%20weeks%20of%20us%20getting%20together.%20I%20said%20it%20knowing%20what%20a%20heavy%20and%20controversial%20topic%20it%20would%20be%20if%20we%20weren't%20careful%20and%20considerate.%20She%20said%20she%20didn't.%20She%20was%20in%20her%20late%2040s%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturning-work-trips-into-vacations-according-to-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etraveled%20extensively%20for%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Bringing%20a%20child%20into%20our%20relationship%20was%20a%20hard%20no%20for%20her.%20It%20was%20then%20up%20to%20me%20to%20decide%20if%20I%20wanted%20a%20child%20more%20than%20I%20wanted%20to%20continue%20loving%20her.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20took%20the%20risk%2C%20and%20it%20paid%20off%20with%20interest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20made%20the%20conscious%20choice%20to%20give%20up%20being%20a%20mother%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-you-know-when-youre-in-love-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esomeone%20I%20was%20falling%20madly%20in%20love%20with%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20still%20talk%20about%20kids%2C%20but%20these%20talks%20look%20different%20now%20as%20we%20navigate%20a%20life%20filled%20with%20experiences%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20if%20we%20had%20had%20children.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20knows%20I%20don't%20hold%20her%20responsible%20for%20my%20empty%20womb.%20And%20I'm%20proud%20of%20her%20for%20standing%20firm%20in%20her%20convictions%2C%20knowing%20the%20burden%20she%20would%20leave%20me%20with%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20commitment%20to%20communication%20and%20our%20happiness%20with%20all%20we%20have%20been%20blessed%20with%20without%20a%20child%2C%20are%20important%20reasons%20we%20are%20child-free%20and%20still%20happily%20married.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22402f650a-53f2-4237-bbba-8f27e42eefcd%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20both%20needed%20emotional%20maturity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20amount%20of%20communication%20was%20going%20to%20be%20successful%20without%20emotional%20maturity.%20If%20we%20couldn't%20start%20from%20a%20place%20of%20love%20and%20understanding%2C%20we%20were%20only%20going%20to%20end%20up%20in%20arguments.%20A%20solid%20foundation%20built%20on%20honoring%20but%20managing%20our%20feelings%20meant%20none%20of%20our%20conversations%20about%20children%20would%20end%20up%20as%20fights.%20My%20wife%20was%20not%20responsible%20for%20me%20not%20having%20a%20child.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20recently%20found%20out%2C%20through%20the%20popular%20ancestry%20website%2C%20that%20an%20egg%20donation%20I%20made%20in%20my%2020s%20resulted%20in%20a%20successful%20pregnancy.%20There%20is%20now%20a%2010-year-old%20boy%20somewhere%20out%20there%20with%20pieces%20of%20me%20woven%20into%20the%20fabric%20of%20his%20existence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20this%20discovery%2C%20my%20wife%20held%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20we%20talked%20about%20our%20feelings.%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20of%20what%20I%20felt%2C%20but%20she%20felt%20apprehension.%20Which%20was%20understandable%20%E2%80%94%20she%20decided%20for%20herself%20she%20didn't%20want%20children%2C%20but%20a%20child%20could%20come%20out%20of%20the%20woodwork%20looking%20for%20me.%20That's%20not%20what%20she%20signed%20up%20for.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20empathized%20with%20her%20feelings%20while%20still%20honoring%20my%20exploration%20of%20whatever%20was%20stirring%20in%20my%20heart.%20And%20no%20fights%20were%20had%20because%20of%20this%20out-of-left-field%20discovery.%20We%20met%20each%20other%20with%20love%20and%20are%20continuing%20to%20process%20this%20news%20united.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20emotional%20maturity%2C%20our%20home%20of%20love%20would%20have%20just%20been%20a%20house%20of%20conflicting%2C%20negative%20emotions.%20And%20without%20complete%20honesty%20in%20our%20communication%2C%20our%20home%20would%20have%20been%20a%20house%20of%20facades%2C%20ready%20to%20crumble%20the%20first%20time%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20a%20child.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20we%20have%20no%20regrets.%20And%20we%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20our%20very%20successful%20child-free%20marriage%2C%20filled%20with%20experiences%2C%20laughter%2C%20love%2C%20and%20dogs%20we%20put%20in%20sweaters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwanted-kids-my-wife-didnt-we-makeour-childfree-relationship-work-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732325162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b9ae0192f5258985936c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwanted-kids-my-wife-didnt-we-makeour-childfree-relationship-work-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20said%20I%20wanted%20kids%20early%20in%20our%20relationship%20and%20my%20wife%20said%20she%20didn't.%20I%20decided%20to%20choose%20her%20instead%20and%20don't%20hold%20it%20against%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Brooke%20Havrilla)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3