0combined%20clients%20range%20from%20blue%20chip%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Amazon%2C%20GM%2C%20and%20Uber%20%E2%80%94%20to%20insurance%20giants%20like%20MetLife%20and%20Fidelity%20National%20Financial.%20Wiles%20and%20Bondi%20were%20also%20separately%20registered%20to%20lobby%20for%20foreign%20interests%2C%20which%20included%20one%20of%20Nigeria's%20largest%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20Qatarian%20embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWiles%20and%20Bondi%20have%20both%20once%20worked%20for%20Ballard%20Partners%2C%20once%20a%20regional%20firm%20in%20Florida%20that%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20due%20to%20its%20ties%20to%20Trump%20world.%20Earlier%20this%20summer%2C%20the%20firm%20opened%20an%20office%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20why%20you%20hired%20Ballard%20Partners%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20is%20knowing%20that%20if%20Trump%20is%20president%2C%20the%20people%20you%20are%20working%20with%20stand%20at%20having%20a%20pretty%20good%20chance%20at%20having%20influence%20in%20a%20Trump%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Hauser%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Revolving%20Door%20Project%2C%20a%20public%20interest%20group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Ballard%2C%20a%20major%20Republican%20fundraiser%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20firm%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292e8e9af-4d6e-464a-a6a1-b591ee745fa6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWiles%20continued%20to%20have%20K-Street%20ties%20as%20she%20helped%20run%20Trump's%20campaign.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWiles%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20did%20not%20cut%20ties%20to%20her%20most%20recent%20firm%20until%20Trump%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20have%20her%20lead%20his%20second%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20past%20work%20included%20an%20effort%20to%20get%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20approve%20a%20cooper%20and%20gold%20mine%20in%20a%20sensitive%20area%20of%20Alaska.%20Sen.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-republican-senators-could-oppose-trump-nominees-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELisa%20Murkowski%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Alaska%20Republican%2C%20widely%20viewed%20as%20a%20key%20vote%20in%20the%20narrowly%20divided%20US%20Senate%2C%20and%20other%20top%20state%20officials%20have%20long%20opposed%20the%20Pebble%20Partnership.%20The%20EPA%2C%20under%20Obama%2C%20Trump%2C%20and%20Biden's%20administrations%2C%20have%20repeatedly%20opposed%20efforts%20to%20mine%20in%20the%20bay%2C%20home%20to%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20salmon%20fisheries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuffy%2C%20who%20if%20confirmed%20would%20oversee%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20lobbied%20in%202020%20for%20an%20airline%20group%20that%20includes%20American%2C%20Delta%2C%20and%20United%20among%20its%20members.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20not%20long%20after%20he%20left%20Congress%20in%202019%2C%20Duffy%20lobbied%20for%20Polaris%2C%20a%20US%20auto%20manufacturer%20known%20its%20off-road%20and%20recreational%20vehicles.%20Former%20lawmakers%20are%20only%20restricted%20from%20lobbying%20Congress%20for%20a%20year%2C%20though%20they%20can%20immediately%20lobby%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20federal%20government.%20According%20to%20his%20disclosures%2C%20Duffy's%20work%20at%20times%20included%20advising%20the%20company%20on%20how%20to%20navigate%20EV%20incentives%20and%20tariffs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProPublica%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Finside-one-huge-companys-mostly-successful-campaign-to-escape-trumps-tariffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Duffy%20lobbied%20White%20House%20trade%20adviser%20Peter%20Navarro%20as%20Polaris%20sought%20to%20win%20exemptions%20to%20tariffs%20on%20the%20parts%20it%20was%20importing.%20ProPublica%20found%20that%20Polaris'%20efforts%2C%20including%20use%20of%20Duffy%2C%20ultimately%20led%20the%20company%20to%20get%20most%20of%20what%20it%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBondi's%20work%20for%20Amazon%20was%20related%20to%20trade%20and%20tariff%20policy%2C%20according%20to%20disclosures.%20She%20also%20lobbied%20for%20General%20Motors%2C%20Uber%2C%20Fidelity%20National%2C%20Carnival%20North%20America%2C%20and%20even%20Major%20League%20Baseball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e38cdad-090b-40fe-a627-fc3d5a5c2123%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20didn't%20start%20the%20revolving%20door%2C%20but%20the%20swamp%20could%20get%20larger.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWiles%2C%20Bondi%2C%20and%20Duffy's%20respective%20work%20all%20fits%20within%20the%20larger%20revolving%20door%20narrative%20that%20dominates%20Washington%2C%20even%20as%20Trump%20portrays%20himself%20as%20ready%20to%20shake%20up%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20Klain%2C%20President%20Biden's%20first%20chief%20of%20staff%20and%20longtime%20adviser%2C%20was%20a%20lobbyist%20for%20Fannie%20Mae%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%20Steve%20Ricchetti%2C%20another%20longtime%20Biden%20fixture%2C%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20lobbying%20that%20top%20Obama%20administration%20officials%20tried%20to%20prevent%20then-Vice%20President%20Biden%20from%20hiring%20him%20after%20the%202008%20election.%20His%20brother%20Jeff%20Ricchetti%2C%20who%20remains%20a%20registered%20lobbyist%2C%20saw%20his%20business%20boom%20after%20Biden%20won%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Barack%20Obama%20initially%20received%20high%20praise%20for%20his%20limits%20on%20hiring%20lobbyists%20who%20had%20recently%20lobbied%20the%20federal%20agency%20they%20sought%20to%20join%2C%20though%20he%20granted%20some%20limited%20waivers%20including%20to%20a%20former%20top%20lobbyist%20to%20Raytheon.%20Ultimately%2C%20Obama%20was%20unable%20to%20stop%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2015%2F12%2Fbarack-obama-revolving-door-lobbying-217042%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolving%20door%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20Politico%20reported%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHauser%20said%20what%20stands%20out%20about%20the%20Trump%20team%20so%20far%20is%20their%20unorthodox%20approach%20to%20the%20transition%2C%20including%20refusing%20to%20sign%20formal%20agreements%20with%20the%20current%20administration%20which%20would%20include%20ethics%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%2C%20like%20Obama%20and%20Biden%2C%20issued%20an%20ethics-related%20executive%20order%20after%20taking%20office%20in%202017%2C%20Hauser%20isn't%20convinced%20it%20will%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20aversion%20of%20his%20transition%20to%20the%20ethics%20process%20of%20the%20transition%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20an%20open%20question%20whether%20or%20not%20he%20is%20going%20to%20make%20his%20appointees%20sign%20additional%20ethics%20pledges%20in%20office%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Hauser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lobbyists-ties-wiles-bondi-duffy-ballard-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732314492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740e93c9f2901eb60367589%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lobbyists-ties-wiles-bondi-duffy-ballard-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20picks%20for%20attorney%20general%2C%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20and%20Transportation%20secretary%20have%20been%20federal%20lobbyists%20for%20major%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lobbyists-ties-wiles-bondi-duffy-ballard-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20wins%20civil%20rape%20case%20against%20Conor%20McGregor%22%2C%22co