20online%20inquiries%20to%20the%20firm%20were%20%26quot%3Bconstant%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20morning%20after%20Election%20Day%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20firm%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20392%25%20increase%20in%20inquiries%20from%20US%20nationals%20during%20election%20week%20compared%20to%20the%20week%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20firms%20operating%20in%20the%20space%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-migration-firms-what-they-are-hearing-after-the-election-2024-11%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArton%20Capital%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20received%20between%20110%20and%20120%20inquiries%20on%20the%20day%20following%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20about%20five%20times%20its%20typical%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aecaef4d-33ce-40a7-8ef5-9b19be474733%5C%22%3EClients%20have%20new%20concerns%20this%20time%20around%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReaz%20Jafri%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20citizenship%20consulting%20firm%20Dasein%2C%20said%20in%20addition%20to%20wanting%20an%20option%20B%2C%20clients%20are%20wanting%20to%20move%20their%20assets%20offshore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20people%20are%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-higher-inflation-fed-interest-rates-taxes-mortgage-rates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20promise%20to%20raise%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20how%20that%20could%20impact%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20US%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeading%20up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20firm%20helped%20a%20number%20of%20clients%20set%20up%20accounts%20in%20Europe%20and%20move%20assets%20offshore%2C%20which%20Jafri%20said%20can%20take%20about%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20to%20evade%20taxes%20or%20hide%20their%20money%2C%20it's%20just%20to%20keep%20it%20out%20of%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20US%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Jafri%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20clients%20want%20to%20ensure%20their%20wealth%20isn't%20held%20solely%20in%20US%20banks%20if%20restrictions%20are%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJafri%20also%20said%20the%20election%20has%20raised%20concerns%20within%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Trump's%20reelection%2C%20Jafri%20said%20he's%20had%20three%20same-sex%20couples%20reach%20out%20to%20him%20because%20of%20worries%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20with%20same-sex%20marriage.%20Another%20client%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20already%20been%20considering%20a%20secondary%20passport%20because%20he%20has%20a%20transgender%20child%20and%20is%20concerned%20about%20their%20rights%20under%20the%20new%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGalst%20reported%20similar%20concerns%20from%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bsort%20of%20particular%20trauma%20in%20certain%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20people%20who%20are%20transgender%20or%20gay%2C%20Galst%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20has%20not%20felt%20that%20in%20conversations%20with%20clients%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cefd7179-fa70-4002-9ca8-ae170569d340%5C%22%3EA%20surge%20in%20interest%20in%20second%20passports%20after%20an%20election%20is%20normal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicha-Rose%20Emmett%2C%20CEO%20of%20London-based%20citizenship%20consultancy%20firm%20CS%20Global%20Partners%2C%20said%20she's%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%20and%20has%20been%20through%20a%20number%20of%20US%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElections%2C%20especially%20those%20since%202016%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20accompanied%20by%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20getting%20anxious%26quot%3B%20about%20which%20political%20party%20is%20going%20to%20win%20and%20searching%20for%20alternatives%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20peaks%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20or%20maybe%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20and%20then%20everything%20goes%20back%20to%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20Emmett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20a%20new%20administration%20impact%20people%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeading%20up%20to%20the%202020%20election%2C%20Jafri%20said%20there%20was%20an%20increase%20in%20interest%20from%20his%20clientele's%20Republican%20contingent.%20They%20were%20concerned%20about%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20or%20a%20similar%20candidate%20coming%20into%20the%20presidency%20and%20the%20impact%20it%20would%20have%20from%20%26quot%3Ba%20tax%20policy%20point%20of%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmmett%20said%20during%20these%20surges%2C%20some%20people%20do%20end%20up%20going%20through%20with%20the%20application%20process.%20However%2C%20they've%20either%20been%20thinking%20about%20it%20for%20a%20while%20or%20there's%20an%20investment%20opportunity%20that%20coincides%20with%20the%20political%20situation%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20super%20high%20net%20worth%20individuals%20it's%20not%20purely%20a%20political%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Emmett%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20factors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecond-passport-application-steps-to-consider-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecondary%20passport%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%20require%20extensive%20paperwork%20and%20can%20cost%20a%20minimum%20of%20%24200%2C000%20per%20application%2C%20with%20the%20more%20expensive%20locations%20costing%20%241%20million%20for%20a%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20don't%20happen%20overnight.%20Some%20programs%20can%20take%20two%20years%20to%20process%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGalst%20said%20that%20many%20people%20seeking%20these%20passports%20are%20thinking%20about%20retirement%20and%20creating%20generational%20opportunities.%20Others%20are%20looking%20to%20diversify%20their%20assets.%20She%20said%20one%20client%20told%20her%20he%20spent%20%241%20million%20on%20insurance%20%E2%80