%20lag%20above%20all%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20start%20planning%20right%20away%20so%20we%20have%20the%20best%20options%20available%20to%20negate%20jet%20lag%20and%20put%20the%20athletes%20in%20the%20best%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4e3e1b8-271e-43eb-b3d5-8613a4520203%5C%22%3EMonitoring%20light%20and%20'zeitgeber'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20fighting%20jet%20lag%2C%20Clark%20said%2C%20there's%20one%20main%20factor%20to%20consider%3A%20exposure%20to%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLight%20from%20the%20sun%20and%20light%20from%20electronic%20devices%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20light%20%E2%80%94%20if%20we%20can%20manipulate%20those%20things%20in%20accordance%20to%20where%20we're%20trying%20to%20travel%2C%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20shift%20the%20body%20clock%20closer%20to%20that%20given%20time%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%2C%20Clark%20points%20to%20Esteban%20Ocon%2C%20the%20Alpine%20driver%20with%20whom%20he%20works%20most%20closely.%20In%20preparation%20for%20heading%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff1-las-vegas-grand-prix-race-cost-fans-economic-boost-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELas%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20%E2%80%94%20about%20a%20nine-hour%20time%20shift%20from%20Ocon's%20home%20in%20Switzerland%20%E2%80%94%20Clark%20began%20shifting%20the%20driver's%20bedtime%20and%20wake-up%20time%20later%20and%20later%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20look%20at%20his%20timing%20to%20light%20exposure%2C%20which%20we%20try%20to%20replicate%20to%20the%20time%20zone%20he's%20traveling%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20basic%20first%20principle%2C%20that's%20what%20we%20do%20fundamentally%20to%20thrive%20in%20the%20new%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alpine%20F1%20performance%20coach%20Tom%20Clark%20puts%20driver%20Esteban%20Ocon%20of%20Alpine%20F1%20through%20a%20hand-eye%20coordination%20exercise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673fdd109f2901eb603646ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Clark%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20Alpine%20driver%20Esteban%20Ocon%20to%20optimize%20his%20performance%20on%20the%20track.%3Cp%3EAlpine%20F1%2FTom%20Clark%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Clark%20closely%20monitors%20Ocon's%20%26quot%3Bzeitgeber%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20German%20word%20for%20external%20circadian%20time%20cues%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20body's%20clock.%20This%20includes%20physical%20activity%20and%20fitness%2C%20socializing%2C%20and%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20those%20have%20an%20influence%20on%20moving%20the%20body%20clock%20closer%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20new%20time%20zone%2C%20Clark%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20light%20that%20is%20the%20most%20influential%2C%20so%20that's%20what%20we%20prioritize%20the%20greatest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284c05143-5120-435f-9a08-9894cd6e17f0%5C%22%3E'Las%20Vegas%20is%20the%20nastiest%20one%20of%20the%20season'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlane%20travel%20is%20another%20factor.%20When%20traveling%20west%2C%20Clark%20wants%20his%20drivers%20to%20take%20daytime%20flights%20so%20that%20they%20stay%20awake.%20When%20flying%20east%2C%20he%20encourages%20them%20to%20sleep%20on%20flights%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20when%20the%20series%20heads%20to%20Australia%2C%20which%20entails%20about%20a%2024-hour%20door-to-door%20travel%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Formula%201%20heading%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20this%20weekend%20to%20kick%20off%20the%20final%20triple-header%20of%20the%20season%2C%20Clark%20said%20the%20battle%20against%20jet%20lag%20would%20be%20particularly%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLas%20Vegas%20is%20the%20nastiest%20one%20of%20the%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20because%20the%20race%20happens%20so%20late%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Grand%20Prix%20begins%20about%2010%20p.m.%20local%20time%20%E2%80%94%20drivers%20have%20to%20modify%20their%20sleep%20schedules%20so%20that%20they%20essentially%20become%20nocturnal%2C%20sleeping%20during%20most%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lewis%20Hamilton%20takes%20his%20F1%20car%20for%20a%20spin%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654bc9dab788914e5552a523%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELewis%20Hamilton%20taking%20his%20F1%20car%20for%20a%20spin%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3EDan%20Istitene%20-%20Formula%201%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20like%20Esteban%20and%20you%20get%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20sleep%2C%20he%20effectively%20will%20sleep%20the%20entire%20daylight%20hours%20of%20Las%20Vegas%20%E2%80%94%20which%20actually%20might%20be%20quite%20a%20normal%20thing%20for%20most%20Vegas%20visitors%20and%20tourists%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20weird%20way%20to%20live%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20necessity%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20sleep%20opportunities%20that%20we%20have.%20We%20use%20other%20means%20to%20help%20with%20what%20we%20lose%20from%20not%20seeing%20the%20sun%2C%20like%20vitamin%20D%20supplements.%20We'll%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20that%20during%20the%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Grand%20Prix%20ends%2C%20the%20series%20immediately%20shifts%20to%20Qatar%2C%20meaning%20every%20team%20member%20once%20again%20has%20to%20rapidly%20adjust%20their%20body%20clocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEffectively%2C%20you're%20doing%20a%20full%20circulation%20of%20the%20globe%20in%20time%20zones%20in%20the%20space%20of%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20Last%20year%2C%20when%20Las%20Vegas%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20triple-header%2C%20many%20people%20discovered%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bcontinually%20be%20in%20a%20state%20of%20sleep%20deprivation%20and%20poor%20quality%20of%20sleep%20if%20you%20don't%20prioritize%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20began%20working%20with%20Alpine%20in%202018%20in%20a%20performance%20role%20and%20said%20he%20viewed%20battling%20jet%20lag%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Belephant%20in%20the%20room%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20came%20to%20race%20prep.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20doing%20everything%20we%20could%20from%20a%20training%2C%20nutrition%2C%20and%20recovery%20standpoint%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20sleep%2C%20there%20wasn't%20much%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20my%20appetite%20came%20from%20to%20pursue%20and%20understand%20jet%20lag%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Formula%201%20teams%2C%20he%20said%2C%20now%20task%20their%20performance%20coaches%20and%20doctors%20with%20monitoring%20drivers'%20sleep%20patterns%20and%20adjusting%20them%20to%20new%20time%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20Formula%201%2C%20Clark%20is%20pursuing%20doctoral%20work%20on%20jet%20lag%20%E2%80%94%20a%20topic%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20not%20studied%20extensively%20in%20academic%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJet%20lag%20itself%20is%20a%20hard%20thing%20to%20research%20and%20understand%20just%20by%20the%20nature%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20study%20it%20in%20a%20lab%20environment%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20replicate%20getting%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20the%20large%20amount%20of%20time%20in%20the%20air%2C%20all%20the%20stresses%20you%20go%20through%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20arriving%20in%20a%20widely%20different%20culture%20and%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20Formula%201%20an%20ideal%20industry%20in%20which%20to%20conduct%20this%20research%2C%20with%20the%20sport%20featuring%20perhaps%20the%20most%20condensed%20global%20travel%20of%20any%20other%20sport%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20working%20within%20the%20Formula%201%20population%20and%20yes%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20easiest%20thing%20to%20fit%20in%20around%20my%20day%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said%2C%20laughing.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20fascinating%2C%20and%20I'm%20enjoying%20it%20very%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-f1-drivers-deal-with-jet-lag-using-sleep-science-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732304691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673fd9b79f2901eb603646d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-f1-drivers-deal-with-jet-lag-using-sleep-science-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Faced%20with%20a%20calendar%20spanning%20multiple%20continents%20and%20time%20zones%2C%20F1%20teams%20employ%20sleep%20experts%20to%20help%20drivers%20overcome%20constant%20jet%20lag.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Gregory%20Leporati)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-f1-drivers-deal-with-jet-lag-using-sleep-science-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plane%20passengers%20film%20Iceland%20volcano%20lava%20from%20above%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732304368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fcde4%2Flive%2F67e57ef0-a8c2-11ef-bdf5-b7cb2fa86e10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcq521pw0pgjo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Down%20below%2C%20a%20car%20park%20was%20swallowed%20up%20by%20lava%20and%20buildings%20were%20evacuated%2C%20but%20there%20was%20said%20to%20be%20no%20threat%20to%20air%20travel%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%