%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20instance%20that%20Smith%20registered%20a%20first%20ball%20duck%20in%20home%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20read%20too%20much%20into%20it%20today.%20I%20mean%20the%20pitch%20is%20doing%20enough%20at%20pace%20and%20Bumrah%20is%20a%20world%20class%20bowler.%20People%20have%20always%20questioned%20Steve%20Smith's%20technique%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20he%20always%20responds.%20He's%20a%20good%20problem%20solver%2C%26quot%3B%20Waugh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20his%20footwork%20at%20times%2C%20he%20can%20go%20too%20far%20across%20(to)%20the%20off-side.%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20something%20he's%20aware%20of.%20But%20I%20think%20today%2C%20the%20first%20ball%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20read%20too%20much%20into%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732296300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F29jk47ho_virat-kohli-in-training-afp_625x300_21_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fbehind-virat-kohlis-perth-test-tactic-england-greats-justification-had-to-do-7081818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20managed%20just%20five%20runs%20before%20fending%20off%20a%20climbing%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20delivery%20to%20Usman%20Khawaja%20at%20slip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fbehind-virat-kohlis-perth-test-tactic-england-greats-justification-had-to-do-7081818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fact%20check%3A%20Did%20Elon%20Musk%20accuse%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20ex-wife%2C%20MacKenzie%20Scott%2C%20of%20'destroying%20Western%20civilization'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732294933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115574209%2Cimgsize-1136175.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi