%20with%20%E2%80%98Copewithcancer%20%E2%80%93%20Madat%20Trust%E2%80%99%20at%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Tata%20Memorial%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Talk%20to%20them%20as%20people%2C%20not%20patients%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Informatics%20and%20Research%2C%20one%20in%20nine%20people%20in%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20at%20some%20point%20in%20their%20lives.%20Beyond%20its%20physical%20toll%2C%20cancer%20profoundly%20affects%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ftop-mental-health-expert-do-you-need-help-get-free-counselling-find-support-manage-stress-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20and%20emotional%20well-being%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20psychological%20support%20vital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20cancer%20patient%20needs%20a%20counsellor%20to%20help%20them%20cope%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alpa%20emphasises.%20She%20points%20out%20that%20families%20often%20withhold%20the%20diagnosis%20from%20patients%2C%20fearing%20they%20might%20lose%20the%20will%20to%20live.%20While%20she%20understands%20their%20perspective%2C%20Alpa%20believes%20patients%20deserve%20honesty%20to%20fulfil%20their%20personal%20and%20familial%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-3_11zon-1732188965.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alpa%20providing%20conselling%20for%20a%20patient%20post%20Bone%20Marrow%20Transplantation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-3_11zon-1732188965.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3