ssions%20and%20promote%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20By%20introducing%20electric%20buses%2C%20Bhubaneswar%20is%20making%20significant%20strides%20in%20improving%20air%20quality%20and%20reducing%20noise%20pollution%20%E2%80%94%20efforts%20that%20align%20with%20global%20trends%20toward%20greener%20public%20transport%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Copenhagen%20has%20integrated%20electric%20buses%20into%20its%20fleet%20as%20part%20of%20its%20goal%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20by%2050%25%20by%202030.%20Similarly%2C%20Singapore%E2%80%99s%20green%20transport%20initiatives%2C%20which%20aim%20to%20electrify%20the%20entire%20bus%20fleet%20by%202040%2C%20echo%20a%20similar%20commitment%20to%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20environmental%20benefits%2C%20the%20Mo%20Bus%20system%20prioritises%20safety%20and%20inclusivity.%20Features%20like%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20emergency%20panic%20buttons%2C%20and%20priority%20seats%20for%20women%20and%20children%20ensure%20that%20passengers%20feel%20secure.%20The%20system%20is%20also%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20seniors%20and%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20making%20it%20accessible%20to%20a%20diverse%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20jobs%20and%20connecting%20communities%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Bhubaneswar%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20inclusivity%20came%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20Mo%20E-Ride%20in%202022.%20This%20eco-friendly%20e-rickshaw%20service%20connects%20people%20to%20bus%20stops%2C%20offering%20affordable%20and%20safe%20last-mile%20connectivity.%20It%20is%20particularly%20beneficial%20for%20elderly%20passengers%2C%20women%2C%20and%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20transport%20network%20serves%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2