ed%20by%20feedback%20from%20the%20farming%20community.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20to%20over%201%2C000%20farmers%2C%20shown%20them%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%2C%20and%20listened%20to%20their%20feedback.%20Through%20countless%20conversations%20and%20research%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gained%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20their%20challenges%20and%20how%20my%20vehicle%20can%20make%20a%20difference.%20The%20joy%20and%20appreciation%20I%20see%20on%20their%20faces%2C%20knowing%20that%20young%20people%20like%20me%20are%20working%20to%20help%20them%2C%20keeps%20me%20motivated%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20future%20plans%20for%20So-Apt%2C%20Suhani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20adding%20a%20GPS%20system%20to%20help%20farmers%20track%20which%20parts%20of%20their%20field%20they%20have%20covered%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20planting%2C%20irrigating%2C%20or%20applying%20fertilisers.%20This%20will%20make%20the%20farming%20process%20more%20efficient.%E2%80%9D%20She%E2%80%99s%20also%20incorporating%20a%20pH%20calculator%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20soil%20healt%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%3Eh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20further%20enhancing%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20functionality%20and%20making%20it%20an%20even%20more%20valuable%20tool%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20making%20the%20vehicle%20smarter%20and%20easier%20to%20use%20for%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20vehicle%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20affordable%20but%20also%20user-friendly.%20Farmers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20op