%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWorkshop%20on%20comprehensive%20fire%20safety%20conducted%20in%20Bhubaneshwar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20Odisha%20offered%20was%20the%20digitisation%20of%20NOCs%2C%20providing%20a%20solid%20database%20to%20identify%20violators%20regarding%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20a%20fire%20accident%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20here%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20be%20lethargic%20in%20applying%20for%20appropriate%20licences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%20that%20simple%20measures%20like%20planning%20the%20electrical%20load%20and%20investing%20in%20appropriate%20wiring%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20switchboard%20placements%2C%20mapping%20the%20escape%20routes%2C%20placing%20a%20fire%20extinguisher%20in%20place%2C%20investing%20in%20a%20fire%20alarm%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20before%20moving%20into%20a%20building%20can%20save%20lives%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264089%2Fdrdo-dare-to-dream-contest-winner-innovation-aircraft-accident-biodegradable%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20such%20disasters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20basics%20of%20fire%20safety%2C%20Venkitachalam%20discusses%20two%20primary%20criteria%3A